# =============================================================================
# Argus API Configuration
# =============================================================================
#
# Priority order (first match wins):
#
# 1. ARGUS config (for proxy services) - both required:
#    ARGUS_ANTHROPIC_API_KEY + ARGUS_ANTHROPIC_BASE_URL
#
# 2. Claude Code OAuth (auto-detected from Claude Code login):
#    ANTHROPIC_AUTH_TOKEN + ANTHROPIC_BASE_URL
#
# 3. Official Anthropic API (uses default endpoint):
#    ANTHROPIC_API_KEY
#
# 4. Config file (~/.argus/config.json)
#
# =============================================================================

# Option 1: Proxy service (e.g., api.dd3.gccode.cn)
# ARGUS_ANTHROPIC_API_KEY=your_proxy_api_key
# ARGUS_ANTHROPIC_BASE_URL=https://your-proxy.example.com

# Option 2: Claude Code OAuth - no config needed if already logged in via `claude login`
# These are auto-detected from your Claude Code session

# Option 3: Official Anthropic API
# ANTHROPIC_API_KEY=sk-ant-your_key_here

# Optional: Override default model (default: claude-opus-4-5-20251101)
# ARGUS_ANTHROPIC_MODEL=claude-opus-4-5-20251101
